### Summary of ASX Announcement (Appendix 3Y - Change of Director’s Interest Notice)  

1. **Director**: Fabrizio Perilli  
   - **Change**: Lapse of 1,200,000 Performance Rights (Class B & D) on 30 June 2025.  
   - **Holding Post-Change**:  
     - 3,553,203 ordinary shares  
     - 250,000 unlisted options (exercisable at $0.15, expiring 14 Nov 2026)  
     - 600,000 Performance Rights (Class C, expiring 31 Dec 2025).  

2. **Director**: Andrew Ferrier  
   - **Change**: Lapse of 1,600,000 Performance Rights (Class B & D) on 30 June 2025.  
   - **Holding Post-Change**:  
     - 1,717,391 ordinary shares  
     - 500,000 unlisted options (exercisable at $0.15, expiring 14 Nov 2026)  
     - 800,000 Performance Rights (Class C, expiring 31 Dec 2025).  

**No material trading impact** (lapsed rights imply unmet performance conditions; no securities issued).
